  "description": "Create English Menu Matching Polish Menu Structure\n\nUpdate the English language menu to contain identical navigation items as the Polish menu, with properly translated labels and localized URLs.\n\nRequirements:\n- Audit the Polish (pl) menu to identify all navigation items and their hierarchy\n- Create corresponding English (en) menu entries with the same structure and order\n- Translate all Polish menu item labels to English accurately\n- Update URLs to use English slugs/paths while maintaining the same destination pages\n- Ensure menu depth and nesting matches exactly between pl and en versions\n- Verify all links are functional and point to the correct English content\n- Maintain consistent styling and behavior across both language versions\n- Test navigation flow to ensure no broken links or missing pages",
